---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Generative Engine Optimisation (GEO) Services Philippines | Bright Forge SEO" description="Future-proof your visibility in AI search results with GEO services in the Philippines. Optimise for ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity and more.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-brain"
    badgeText="GEO Specialists"
    title="Generative Engine Optimisation (GEO) Services Philippines"
    breadcrumbCurrent="Generative Engine Optimization Philippines"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>Future-Proof Your Visibility in AI Search Results in the Philippines</p>

      <p>As ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, and other generative AI tools reshape how people find information in the Philippines and globally, traditional SEO alone isn't enough. Your potential clients are asking AI assistants for recommendations, and if your business isn't optimised for these platforms, you're invisible to an entire segment of search behaviour.</p>

      <p>Generative Engine Optimisation (GEO) ensures your content appears when AI tools answer queries in your industry. It's not about gaming algorithms—it's about structuring your expertise so AI systems can accurately cite and recommend your business.</p>

      <p>Our <strong>Generative Engine Optimization Philippines</strong> services help businesses dominate AI-powered search results with <strong>professional GEO strategies</strong>. From ChatGPT optimization to AI-powered content structuring, we position your brand as the authoritative source in the Philippines as your trusted <strong>GEO partner</strong>, so you can capture more visibility and citations in generative AI responses.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Get Your Free GEO Audit" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#why-geo" text="Learn About GEO" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="geo-icon-grid">
          <div class="geo-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="geo-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="geo-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="geo-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="geo-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="geo-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Why GEO Matters Section -->
  <section class="challenges-section" id="why-geo">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Why Now</div>
        <h2>Why GEO Matters <span>Now in the Philippines</span></h2>
        <p>The landscape has shifted dramatically. Over 40% of searches now involve AI-powered answers, and that figure is climbing monthly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="challenges-content">
        <div class="challenge-text">
          <p>When someone in the Philippines asks ChatGPT or Perplexity "Who provides [your service] in [your location]?", you need to be in that response.</p>
          <p>Traditional SEO optimises for search engine results pages. GEO optimises for AI-generated answers. The techniques overlap, but the execution differs. AI models prioritise different signals: structured data, authoritative citations, clear expertise demonstration, and content that directly answers complex queries.</p>

          <p><strong>If you're not thinking about how AI interprets your content, you're already behind competitors who are.</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="challenge-image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?w=800&q=80" alt="AI Search and Generative Engine Optimization" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach Section -->
  <section class="edge-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Our Approach</div>
        <h2>Our Approach to <span>Generative Engine Optimisation</span></h2>
        <p>We've spent 15+ years understanding how search engines evaluate content. Now we're applying that expertise to how AI models process, cite, and recommend businesses in the Philippines.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="edge-content">
        <p><strong>We focus on three core pillars:</strong></p>

        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Authority Signals That AI Models Recognise</h3>
            <p>AI systems look for expertise markers: structured data, author credentials, industry recognition, and content depth. We optimise your digital footprint so generative engines understand your authority in your field.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Content Structured for AI Interpretation</h3>
            <p>Generative models favour content that clearly answers questions, provides evidence, and follows logical information hierarchies. We restructure your existing content and create new pieces specifically formatted for AI parsing.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Citation-Worthy Content Development</h3>
            <p>When AI systems generate responses, they cite sources they trust. We develop content that's quotable, accurate, and positioned to earn citations in AI-generated answers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="edge-conclusion">This isn't guesswork. We test, measure, and refine based on how your content performs across ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, and other platforms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included Section -->
  <section class="solution-section-new">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">What's Included</div>
        <h2>Your Complete <span>GEO Solution</span></h2>
        <p>At Bright Forge SEO, we've developed a comprehensive GEO methodology to position our clients in the Philippines as industry leaders.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-grid-geo">
        <div class="process-box-geo orange-bg">
          <div class="process-number-geo">1</div>
          <div class="process-icon-geo">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>GEO Audit & Strategy</h3>
          <p>We analyse how your current content performs in AI search results, identify gaps where competitors appear instead of you, and develop a comprehensive optimisation strategy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-geo white-bg">
          <div class="process-number-geo">2</div>
          <div class="process-icon-geo">
            <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Technical Implementation</h3>
          <p>Structured data enhancement, schema markup optimisation, and site architecture adjustments to improve AI crawlability and interpretation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-geo orange-bg">
          <div class="process-number-geo">3</div>
          <div class="process-icon-geo">
            <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Content Optimisation</h3>
          <p>We retrofit your existing high-value content for AI citation potential and develop new content designed to answer the complex, conversational queries users pose to AI assistants.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-geo white-bg">
          <div class="process-number-geo">4</div>
          <div class="process-icon-geo">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>AI Platform Monitoring</h3>
          <p>Ongoing tracking of how your business appears in responses from major generative AI platforms, with monthly reporting on visibility improvements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-geo orange-bg">
          <div class="process-number-geo">5</div>
          <div class="process-icon-geo">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Competitive Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Regular analysis of which competitors are winning AI citations in your space and strategic recommendations to overtake them.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-geo white-bg">
          <div class="process-number-geo">6</div>
          <div class="process-icon-geo">
            <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Citation Optimization</h3>
          <p>Strategic content development focused on becoming the most cited source in your industry for AI-generated responses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Can Expect Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section-new">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Timeline</div>
        <h2>What You Can <span>Expect</span></h2>
        <p>GEO, like traditional SEO, requires sustained effort. But the businesses that invest now will dominate AI search results for years whilst competitors in the Philippines scramble to catch up.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-layout-new">
        <div class="benefits-visual-new">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Generative Engine Optimization timeline and results"
            class="benefits-image-new"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="benefits-grid-new">
          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Short Term (1-3 Months)</h3>
            <p>Foundation work: technical implementation, initial content optimisation, and baseline measurement of current AI visibility.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Medium Term (3-6 Months)</h3>
            <p>Increasing appearances in AI-generated responses for your core services, measurable growth in AI referral traffic, and improved positioning against direct competitors.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-crown"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Long Term (6-12 Months)</h3>
            <p>Dominant presence in AI responses for your key topics, established authority signals recognised across platforms, and consistent citation advantage over competitors.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Future-Proof Strategy</h3>
            <p>We're transparent about timelines because GEO requires sustained effort. AI models don't update instantly, and building genuine authority takes time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="choose-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">The Difference</div>
        <h2>The <span>Bright Forge Difference</span></h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Your GEO Experts in the Philippines</p>
      </div>

      <div class="choose-grid">
        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Proven Testing & Refinement</h3>
          <p>Most agencies are still figuring out what GEO means. We've been testing and refining AI optimisation strategies for over two years, tracking which techniques actually move the needle versus which are just theoretical.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>15+ Years SEO Expertise</h3>
          <p>Our approach combines 15+ years of proven SEO expertise with cutting-edge AI platform knowledge. We don't just understand how search engines work—we understand how AI models process information, make recommendations, and cite sources.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Backed Strategies</h3>
          <p>Every recommendation is backed by data. Every strategy is tested. Every report shows measurable improvement in how AI platforms present your business.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Philippines Market Focus</h3>
          <p>We understand the unique needs of businesses in the Philippines, ensuring your GEO strategy is tailored for both local and global AI search visibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Investment Section -->
  <section class="investment-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Investment</div>
        <h2>Investment & <span>Terms</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="investment-content">
        <div class="investment-card">
          <div class="investment-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Starting Investment</h3>
          <p>GEO services start at <strong>16 hours monthly ($480 USD at $30/hour)</strong> for ongoing optimisation and monitoring.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="investment-card">
          <div class="investment-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Commitment</h3>
          <p>Given the strategic nature of the work and time required to influence AI platform behaviour, we require a <strong>minimum six-month commitment</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="investment-card">
          <div class="investment-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <p>Strategy development, technical implementation, content optimisation, and comprehensive monthly reporting on AI visibility metrics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">FAQ</div>
        <h2>Frequently Asked <span>Questions about GEO</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What is the difference between GEO and AEO?</h3>
          <p>While Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) focuses on traditional answer boxes and featured snippets, Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) specifically targets AI-powered generative platforms like ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, and Perplexity. GEO requires deeper content structuring for AI interpretation and citation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How long does it take to see results from GEO?</h3>
          <p>Initial visibility improvements can appear within 1-3 months for technical implementations. Meaningful citation appearances typically emerge at 3-6 months, with dominant positioning achieved at 6-12 months. AI platforms update continuously, so consistent optimisation is essential.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is GEO relevant for my industry in the Philippines?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. Any industry where customers ask questions and seek recommendations can benefit from GEO. Whether you're in e-commerce, professional services, healthcare, or B2B, positioning yourself for AI citations provides a significant competitive advantage in the Philippines market.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will GEO replace traditional SEO?</h3>
          <p>No, GEO complements traditional SEO. A strong technical foundation, quality backlinks, and excellent user experience remain crucial. GEO is an essential layer on top of solid SEO that prepares you for the future of AI-driven search.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="cta-container">
        <h2>Ready to Dominate AI Search Results in the Philippines?</h2>
        <p>The businesses that optimise for generative AI now will have an insurmountable advantage over those who wait. Your competitors in the Philippines are either already investing in GEO or will be within months.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="cta-button">Get Your Free GEO Audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <ContactSection />

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
/* GEO Icon Grid (used in Hero visual slot) */
.hero-image-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 500px;
}

.geo-icon-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.geo-icon {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}

.geo-icon:nth-child(odd) {
  animation-delay: 1s;
}

.geo-icon:nth-child(even) {
  animation-delay: 2s;
}

.geo-icon:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
}

.geo-icon i {
  font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free" !important;
  font-weight: 900 !important;
  font-style: normal !important;
  font-variant: normal !important;
  text-rendering: auto !important;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale !important;
  display: inline-block !important;
  color: white !important;
  font-size: 1.5rem !important;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .geo-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .geo-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .geo-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}

/* Challenges Section Styles */
.challenges-section {
  padding: 80px 0;
  background: #f9f9f9;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.section-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.section-header h2 span {
  color: #f97316;
}

.section-header p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #666;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.section-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  color: white;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
